WEBVTT

00:02.070 --> 00:04.368
(indistinct conversations)

00:07.300 --> 00:09.734
Hey, all I did was give you
some fresh eyes.

00:09.770 --> 00:11.567
Ms. Watson.

00:11.610 --> 00:13.635
I didn't know you and Holmes
were stopping by.

00:13.680 --> 00:15.272
He's not here, just me.

00:15.310 --> 00:16.641
Everything okay?

00:16.680 --> 00:19.376
Uh, could we talk privately?

00:19.420 --> 00:21.411
I haven't heard from him
in over three hours.

00:21.450 --> 00:22.712
He's not responding to texts,

00:22.750 --> 00:24.581
he's not answering his phone.

00:24.620 --> 00:27.612
All due respect, but you know
your boss is a weirdo, right?

00:27.660 --> 00:31.221
He's probably out trying
to find Jimmy Hoffa

00:31.260 --> 00:32.796
in some, uh, subway tunnel.

00:32.830 --> 00:35.253
You don't understand.
We have an arrangement.

00:35.300 --> 00:37.165
We're not supposed to be apart
for more than two hours,

00:37.200 --> 00:38.792
and he's never
supposed to be unreachable.

00:38.830 --> 00:41.264
I know you two are pretty close
for an assistant and a boss,

00:41.300 --> 00:42.699
but how is that even possible?

00:42.740 --> 00:44.401
You both have to sleep, right?

00:44.440 --> 00:46.635
I'm... not his assistant.

00:46.680 --> 00:49.274
I... okay, the only reason
we are together all the time

00:49.310 --> 00:51.198
is because I live at his place.

00:51.250 --> 00:53.810
Okay.

00:53.850 --> 00:57.581
Don't know why you guys couldn't
have just told me that,

00:57.620 --> 00:59.110
but... fine.

00:59.160 --> 01:00.559
Okay, it's not like that.

01:00.590 --> 01:03.150
It's... we're not
together together.

01:03.190 --> 01:05.181
Okay, what is it like?

01:06.400 --> 01:08.288
(sighs)

01:08.330 --> 01:09.490
I-I...

01:09.530 --> 01:11.168
I-I can't say, I'm sorry.

01:11.200 --> 01:12.861
Well, Ms. Watson, if you
want me to help you,

01:12.900 --> 01:15.232
you're gonna have to tell me
what the story is, all right?

01:24.350 --> 01:25.749
I'm a sober companion.

01:25.780 --> 01:27.577
I work with recovering
drug addicts.

01:27.620 --> 01:29.247
Sherlock is my client.

01:29.290 --> 01:31.246
His father hired me
to help him stay clean.

01:31.290 --> 01:33.110
The only reason
I am telling you this

01:33.160 --> 01:34.718
is because I think
he may have relapsed.

01:34.760 --> 01:36.785
I need your help to find him.

01:38.830 --> 01:41.355
(vehicle drives past)

01:45.230 --> 01:47.562
Mm.

02:20.470 --> 02:21.767
(woman laughs)

02:21.800 --> 02:23.358
She's good.
She's great.

02:23.410 --> 02:24.866
Enough about her;
how are you?

02:24.910 --> 02:26.730
I'm good.
Yeah?

02:26.780 --> 02:28.236
Any new men in your life?

02:28.280 --> 02:29.702
Uh, sort of.

02:29.750 --> 02:31.445
But it's work,
I'm not dating anyone.

02:31.480 --> 02:32.708
Good.

02:32.750 --> 02:34.308
Maybe you won't be
as mad at me.

02:34.350 --> 02:35.874
What are you talking about?

02:35.920 --> 02:37.444
You split up with Ty
a while ago,

02:37.490 --> 02:38.741
and you never let me
set you up, so...

02:38.790 --> 02:40.257
Oh, Aaron!

02:40.290 --> 02:41.882
Hi! Over here.

02:41.920 --> 02:43.729
Are you serious?
Shut up.

02:43.760 --> 02:45.921
I'm gonna kill you.
Hey, Em.
Hi!

02:45.960 --> 02:48.451
Oh, I didn't realize
you were meeting someone else.

02:48.500 --> 02:49.592
Yeah, that's okay.
She didn't know, either.

02:49.630 --> 02:50.927
This is Aaron, from work.

02:50.970 --> 02:52.892
EMILY:
Have a seat.

02:52.940 --> 02:55.261
This is Joan, my oldest friend.
Was.

02:55.300 --> 02:57.507
Okay, I've got water
aerobics in 20 minutes.

02:57.540 --> 02:59.770
Wait, wait, I...
I know you two
are strangers, but...

02:59.810 --> 03:01.801
you're both fantastic,
and single, so...

03:01.840 --> 03:03.205
start with that.

03:03.250 --> 03:04.478
See where it goes.

03:04.510 --> 03:07.968
My treat.

03:08.020 --> 03:10.443
I think this is what
you call an ambush setup.

03:10.490 --> 03:11.889
Well, the good news is that I
don't have to buy you a drink.

03:11.920 --> 03:14.218
That's true.
Although I could go for

03:14.260 --> 03:15.682
a double vodka rocks
right about now.

03:15.720 --> 03:18.518
Do you normally drink
spirits before, um, what?

03:18.560 --> 03:20.596
10:00 in the morning?
No, but...

03:20.630 --> 03:22.894
go easy on me,
I've just been ambushed.

03:22.930 --> 03:24.329
(laughs)

03:24.370 --> 03:26.736
WOMAN:
Vanilla latte for... Aaron?

03:26.770 --> 03:28.294
Excuse me, that's me.

03:28.340 --> 03:30.661
Okay.

03:40.550 --> 03:42.586
(phone chimes)

03:42.620 --> 03:44.508
* There you are,
you and your friends *

03:44.550 --> 03:46.916
* Standing in a field
that's... *

03:46.960 --> 03:48.916
Sorry to snoop, but...

03:48.960 --> 03:51.485
"YT? ND U ASAP?"

03:51.530 --> 03:53.623
What, are you texting
with a teenager?

03:53.660 --> 03:55.594
A fully-grown adult, actually.

03:55.630 --> 03:57.825
Sorry, I haven't
done this in a while.

03:57.870 --> 04:00.589
Um... I don't know
where to start.

04:00.640 --> 04:02.938
Me neither.

04:02.970 --> 04:04.369
(phone chimes)

04:04.410 --> 04:07.573
Oh... "CUS"?

04:07.610 --> 04:08.975
I'm guessing that's
"see you soon,"

04:09.010 --> 04:11.899
but what is "IMLTHO"?

04:11.950 --> 04:14.646
HOLMES:
It means "In my less

04:14.680 --> 04:15.840
than humble opinion."

04:15.880 --> 04:18.417
Your abbreviations are becoming
borderline indecipherable.

04:18.450 --> 04:19.986
I don't know why,

04:20.020 --> 04:22.989
because you are obviously
capable of being articulate.

04:23.030 --> 04:24.679
Language is evolving, Watson,

04:24.730 --> 04:26.698
becoming a more efficient
version of itself.

04:26.730 --> 04:28.721
I love text shorthand.

04:28.760 --> 04:30.967
It allows you to convey content
and tone

04:31.000 --> 04:32.831
without losing velocity.

04:32.870 --> 04:34.462
Met a man, I see.

04:35.470 --> 04:36.835
A handsome one, at that.

04:36.870 --> 04:38.838
Um, this is the part
where I ask you

04:38.870 --> 04:40.076
how you knew that, right?

04:40.110 --> 04:41.429
You put your hair up

04:41.480 --> 04:42.879
when you want to look your best.

04:42.910 --> 04:44.446
