04:44.480 --> 04:46.573
You're wrong, of course.
RSadmw.

04:46.620 --> 04:48.474
But it was down when you left
for coffee, and now it's up.

04:48.520 --> 04:50.545
Ergo, you unexpectedly
met a man

04:50.590 --> 04:51.716
you found attractive.

04:51.750 --> 04:53.308
Okay, what am I
doing here, anyway?

04:53.360 --> 04:54.554
You said it couldn't wait?

04:54.590 --> 04:57.081
I'm just trying to
stick to the terms
of our agreement.

04:57.130 --> 04:58.722
You said we're not
supposed to be apart

04:58.760 --> 05:00.091
for more than two hours,

05:00.130 --> 05:01.791
and I have a mysterious
errand to run,

05:01.830 --> 05:03.525
and I have no idea
how long it's gonna take.

05:03.570 --> 05:04.798
What kind of errand?

05:04.830 --> 05:06.559
We have been summoned
to a meeting

05:06.600 --> 05:08.534
of the Board of Directors
of Canon-Ebersole.

05:08.570 --> 05:10.800
The investment ﬁrm. What do
