of 12, shall we say?

06:53.480 --> 06:54.902
You're wondering
if I'm worth it.

06:54.940 --> 06:57.079
I could provide a demonstration,
if you'd like.

06:57.110 --> 06:58.577
I'm fairly sure,

06:58.610 --> 06:59.770
for example,
that these two are

06:59.820 --> 07:01.617
sleeping with each other.

07:01.650 --> 07:02.844
You really should be more
careful of your body language.

07:02.890 --> 07:04.118
And you, for some reason,

07:04.150 --> 07:05.617
have recently used a solvent

07:05.650 --> 07:08.483
to remove fingernail polish
from your hands.

07:08.520 --> 07:10.852
12 times your usual rate
will be just fine.

07:10.890 --> 07:14.018
I will need access to Peter
Talbott's office, his computer.

07:14.060 --> 07:17.166
My secretary will be happy to
take you down there right now.

07:24.070 --> 07:25.765
Cute couple.

07:25.810 --> 07:27.038
WOMAN:
Everyone here calls
Peter and Alyssa

07:27.080 --> 07:28.638
"Taylor and Burton."

07:28.680 --> 07:29.908
You know,
after the movie stars.

07:29.950 --> 07:31.144
Fascinating.

07:31.180 --> 07:34.809
