actually.

07:41.520 --> 07:43.021
I think I could've got
20 times my normal rate.

07:43.060 --> 07:46.029
What is your normal rate?
Oh, I don't have one.

07:46.060 --> 07:47.925
Remind me to make one up
before I leave.

07:47.960 --> 07:49.496
Typical.

07:49.530 --> 07:51.168
Every stuffed shirt who
wants to pass for erudite

07:51.200 --> 07:52.758
