consults all the time.

08:12.090 --> 08:13.580
Ah.

08:13.620 --> 08:15.815
I've never been a fan of
John Maynard Keynes,

08:15.860 --> 08:17.521
but this I could
sink my teeth into.

08:17.560 --> 08:18.754
WATSON:
I don't understand.
What is that?

08:18.790 --> 08:20.291
